fields.descriptive_line: Sketchbook of work by Julie Verhoeven
fields.physical_description: A hard-backed sketchbook used as a sketchbook and scrapbook by Julie Verhoeven. The outer cover is entirely covered with a collage of cuttings from magazines, as well as ribbon, plastic, and pencil sharpenings. The pages of the book are filled with pencil sketches, hand-written notes, printed postcards and images from magazines, as well as fabric cuttings and personal memorabila such as cinema tickets and a broken credit card. Some pages have been left blank.
